Package GoNature

Class AvailableOrders

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.AvailableOrders
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class AvailableOrders
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    AvailableOrders represents information about available orders for booking at a specific park on a given date and time. This class stores details such as the park name, date, time slot, and exit time. This class is typically used to represent available booking slots that customers can reserve.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
    See Also:
